        "text": "Our trademarked M&A&O® approach is a unique combination of people and process that integrates operations at the root level of everything we do. It is disciplined and process-oriented, and has been market- and cycle- tested for more than 29 years.\n\nM&A&O® is a proprietary approach that helps us create value at every stage of an\n\ninvestment, from beginning to end.\n\nM&A&O Analysis\n\nThe M&A&O team is involved from the beginning, starting as early as the management presentation.\n\nM&A&O Execution\n\nThe M&A&O team develops a value creation plan while a dedicated capital markets team works in tandem to build the optimal capital structure.\n\nExit\n\nOnce a company completes its transition, Platinum Equity's dedicated sell-side team works with the operating council to find the right monetization opportunities.\n\nReal Operators\n\nThe \"O\" is in our DNA. We have a large in-house team with real-world industry experience. M&A Operations professionals dig in to create value at the earliest stages of diligence, while Portfolio Operations specialists manage transitions and drive ongoing transformation programs. They know how to effect change from the ground up, with hands-on expertise across a broad range of functional areas."
